In the absolute and incredible vastness that is Marvel's Multiverse, one show dares to explore alternate timelines in said multiverse and show what would happen if major moments from the MCU films we know and love, occurred differently. What If dares to take a peek at other universes where a single change seemingly changes the events of everything that follows. Did the premise work? What are our favorite episodes? What stories would we like to see continue?  Join us in this spoiler-heavy recap and review of What If Season 1 and find out!

